hompson. It features garbage collection, goroutines for concurrency, and a simple syntax that compiles quickly."], "scores": [0.7909909968181859, 0.6823679699416305, 0.6605137104553123, 0.6602207918207401, 0.6584501314396203], "model_name": "bge-large", "document_ids": ["Rust", "C++", "Java", "Lua", "Go"]}}